agentData.mission: Create a minimal Python package (e.g., `qg_bench/`) with a CLI (`run_benchmark`) that: (i) loads `schema.json`, (ii) ingests a small example dataset, (iii) computes 1–2 benchmark observables, and (iv) writes a standardized results JSON plus a deterministic hash/metadata block.
